description: This file declares APIs for the XHFW object related to the Data Model Library, including getter and setter functions for various parameter types, as well as validation, commit, and rollback operations. It also contains licensing and module information.

methods.name: XHFW_GetParamStringValue
methods.description: Retrieves a string parameter value for the XHFW object based on the provided parameter name.

methods.name: XHFW_GetParamBoolValue
methods.description: Retrieves a boolean parameter value for the XHFW object.

methods.name: XHFW_GetParamUlongValue
methods.description: Retrieves an unsigned long parameter value for the XHFW object.

methods.name: XHFW_GetParamIntValue
methods.description: Retrieves an integer parameter value for the XHFW object.

methods.name: XHFW_SetParamStringValue
methods.description: Sets a string parameter value for the XHFW object.

methods.name: XHFW_SetParamBoolValue
methods.description: Sets a boolean parameter value for the XHFW object.

methods.name: XHFW_SetParamUlongValue
methods.description: Sets an unsigned long parameter value for the XHFW object.

methods.name: XHFW_SetParamIntValue
methods.description: Sets an integer parameter value for the XHFW object.

methods.name: XHFW_Commit
methods.description: Commits the changes made to the XHFW object parameters.
